<title>UK: Hague to announce leadership bid on Wednesday - Sky.</title>
<headline>Hague to announce leadership bid on Wednesday - Sky.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-05-06</dateline>
<text>
<p>William Hague will announce on Wednesday his intention to stand in the battle to succeed John Major as leader of the Conservative Party, Sky television said on Tuesday.</p>
<p>Hague, 36, was Welsh Secretary in the Conservative government beaten in the May 1 election by the Labour Party.</p>
